Subject: &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19222&quot; title=&quot;&amp;#39;umount -f&amp;#39; of bind mount marks all imports inactive&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-19222&quot;&gt;LU-19222&lt;/a&gt; llite: disable container &apos;unmount -f&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
